    dek: `You've got the skills — now here's how to run them like a pipeline: organizing your shots, working at full quality, rendering the right formats, and delivering finished VFX back into your edit so nothing loses resolution or falls out of sync. The unglamorous discipline that keeps a VFX project from collapsing.`,
